node.text:
THE BOX Bar Stool

Functional Art by @bakerstreetboys_london

THE BOX Collection is a set of sculptural objects representing the collaboration between the artists and the creative forces of nature.

'Ordinary' rust transformed into luxury pattern unveils here its deep, meditative nature.

The unpredictable reactions of rust guide the artists through the process which makes the nature co-creator of the design.
